../dali-guide_auto/cache/parsed_doxygen/dali-core.json:27874:      "detailed": "Uses a single contiguous allocation (calloc) for the entry table. Power-of-2 capacity, grows at 75% load. Deletion uses tombstones. Key requirements: Must be trivially copyable (stored by value in entries). Must support comparison to sentinels via ==. OpenHashMapTraits<Key> must provide Empty() and Tombstone() sentinels that are distinct from each other and from any valid key.",
../dali-guide_auto/cache/parsed_doxygen/dali-core.json:28089:          "signature": "bool Empty() const",
