\n    \"avoid_symbols\": [],\n    \"id\": \"view_animation\",\n    \"intent\": \"Animate a View using the dali-ui app-facing animation API.\",\n    \"preferred_symbols\": [\n      \"Dali::Ui::View::Animate\"\n    ],\n    \"property_values\": [\n      \"Dali::Actor::Property::OPACITY\",\n      \"Dali::Actor::Property::POSITION\",\n      \"Dali::Actor::Property::SCALE\"\n    ],\n    \"source\": \"generation_config\",\n    \"usage_note\": \"Use View as the object being animated. Inherited transform property enums are owned by Dali::Actor::Property.\"\n  }\n]\n\nConstraints:\n{\n  \"avoid_idioms_unless_needed\": [\n    \"raw_actor_set_property\"\n  ],\n  \"forbidden_claims\": [],\n  \"prefer_idioms\": [\n    \"dali_ui_animation_bridge\",\n    \"fluent_chaining\",\n    \"typed_setters\",\n    \"view_tree\"\n  ]\n}\n\nShort verified evidence snippets:\n- repos/dali-ui/samples/animation/animation-example.cpp:12 (sample, score=1.0)\n```cpp\n* See the License for the specific language governing permissions and\n * limitations under the License.\n */\n\n#include <dali-ui-foundation/dali-ui-foundation.h>\n\nusing namespace Dali;\nusing namespace Dali::Ui;\nusing Dali::Ui::View;\n\n/**\n * Demonstrates the typed animation API with both Bridge and Spec patterns.\n *\n * - Tap the red box: fade out using View-first Bridge pattern\n * - Tap the blue box: fade in using Spec-first pattern\n */\nclass AnimationExample : public ConnectionTracker\n{\npublic:\n  AnimationExample(Application& application)\n  : mApplication(application)\n  {\n    mApplication.InitSignal().Connect(this, &AnimationExample::Create);\n  }\n```\n\n- repos/dali-ui/samples/image-view/animated-image-view-example.cpp:21 (sample, score=1.0)\n```cpp\nusing namespace Dali;\nusing namespace Dali::Ui;\n\n/**\n * AnimatedImageView sample.\n *\n * Demonstrates:\n *   - Play / Pause / Stop / JumpToFrame\n *   - Change Image  (cycles through WebP, GIF×2, URL array)\n *   - LoopCount  (infinite / 3 / 1)\n *   - FrameSpeedFactor  (0.5× / 1.0× / 2.0×)\n *   - StopBehavior  (CURRENT / FIRST / LAST)\n *   - SetFrameDelay  (200ms / 500ms / 1000ms / 2000ms)\n *   - GetPlayState / GetCurrentFrame / GetTotalFrame  (logged on each button press)\n *   - AnimationFinishedSignal\n *\n * Image sources:\n *   0. dog-anim.webp          (animated WebP)\n *   1. dali-logo-anim.gif     (animated GIF)\n *   2. animatedLoading.gif    (animated GIF)\n *   3. URL Array: dog-anim-001~008.png     (8 PNG frames via SetResourceUrls)\n *   4. URL Array: dali-logo-anim-001~015.png  (15 PNG frames via SetResourceUrls)\n *\n```\n\nOptional source files to inspect if needed:\n[\n  {\n    \"kind\": \"sample\",\n    \"lookup_instruction\": \"Open this file only if more concrete usage evidence is needed.\",\n    \"matched_symbols\": [\n      \"Add\",\n      \"AlphaFunction\",\n      \"Animate\",\n      \"Animation\",\n      \"Application\",\n      \"Apply\",\n      \"ApplyTo\",\n      \"BackgroundColor\",\n      \"ConnectionTracker\",\n      \"InputEvent\",\n      \"New\",\n      \"Opacity\",\n      \"Play\",\n      \"PositionY\",\n      \"View\",\n      \"ViewAnimationSpec\"\n    ],\n    \"path\": \"repos/dali-ui/samples/animation/animation-example.cpp\",\n    \"relevance\": \"strong\",\n    \"score\": 1.0,\n    \"selection_reason\": \"symbol_and_path_match\",\n    \"snippet_end_line\": 91,\n    \"snippet_start_line\": 12\n  },\n  {\n    \"kind\": \"sample\",\n    \"lookup_instruction\": \"Open this file only if more concrete usage evidence is needed.\",\n    \"matched_symbols\": [\n      \"Add\",\n      \"Animation\",\n      \"Application\",\n      \"Apply\",\n      \"ConnectionTracker\",\n      \"DownCast\",\n      \"GetState\",\n      \"InputEvent\",\n      \"New\",\n      \"Pause\",\n      \"Play\",\n      \"SetLoopCount\",\n      \"Stop\",\n      \"View\"\n    ],\n    \"path\": \"repos/dali-ui/samples/image-view/animated-image-view-example.cpp\",\n    \"relevance\": \"strong\",\n    \"score\": 1.0,\n    \"select